CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Grupo Aeroportuario del Centro Norte operates airports in the central region of Mexico. The largest airport is in Monterrey, which serves nearly half of the company's total passengers. In addition, the company manages two hotels and one industrial park.
